Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky and Robin have been\Ntaken to the Tower of Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel on top of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised to see you survived that\Naccident eight years ago, Cutty Flam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goals can't be achieved without sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're working in order to\Nensure peace for all of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san put his life on the line\Nto protect the blueprints
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because idiots like you exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time, Luffy was\Nfighting against 10,000 soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the main island of Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Spandam! Please come in!\NPlease advise us on countermeasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Zoro and the others,\Nwho had been waiting on Rocketman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the gates to be opened, charged in\Nafter thorough preparation and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This is terrible!\NWe're gonna crash into the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?! What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dodge it, Kokoro-san!\N--What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There's a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they passed over the main gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed straight to\Nthe main island front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big bazooka unit, step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry up or Robin will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll try that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did we do it?\N--He fell into the waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! He's still clinging onto the edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! If you surrender\Npeacefully, we can pull you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stubborn! Fall into the waterfall already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Give me a foot here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he went over to your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Straw Hat! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, what a crazy place I wandered off into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I was able to take care of a\Nlot of them at once, I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, I should move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,towards that serious looking building, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right!\N--He went that way! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Climb up in order,\Nstarting with those at the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly, okay?! Slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me! It was a wind gust!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just wind! Stop it with your willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:51.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:03.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cross this endless sea to go in search of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:09.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a global miracle no one\Nhas yet been able to find
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:14.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our hearts pounding,\Nwe'll just charge ahead as we please
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:21.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,following the footprints of\Nthose who chase their dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:27.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how stormy the night,\Nif we join our hearts as one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:31.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we will be able to make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:39.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:45.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there are tears\Nwe don't want anyone to see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:51.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Nif we want to achieve our dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we should always look\Nstraight ahead without fear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:09.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nhead past everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:15.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as we don't run from it,\Nwe can grasp tomorrow in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:21.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Neverything we see before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:26.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's carve it into the blank pages of our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Brand New World
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:44.04,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Catch Up with Luffy!\NThe Straw Hats' All-Out Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! I know who that swordsman is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's one of Straw Hat's\Nunderlings, Pirate Hunter Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called you an underling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're even lower\Nthan that, right, "Pirate A"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, "B."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! If I had a bounty, it'd be\Nat least twice as much as yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, "C."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to what I'm saying, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking, they can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of my plan, Chopper-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, I didn't know.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more of them in the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have to be more!\NBlow it up before they come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it! Nami-san is still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards! I'm gonna\Ncut them into three pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Pirate A.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An attack like that isn't enough\Nto take someone like her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only "Pirate A" because you\Ndon't get something as obvious as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn Moss Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, that scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Sogeking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm okay, Chopper-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look at that!\N--Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I'm a senior citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a child and here is a\Nsmall animal! We're weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Pirates threatened me\Nand made me operate the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who lets their hostages drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! We almost\Nkilled the hostages, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people, to think that those\Npirates took a senior, a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a small animal hostage... How despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! That smoke looks like clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using cool balls and heat balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the moisture in the air is turned into clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! So you escaped the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the cloud is getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, Grandma. The cloud is getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cloud looks a little dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney, Gonbe. Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure wasn't named the\N"Perfect Clima Takt" for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It develops much bigger clouds now,\Nand it does it much faster too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm gonna see how\Npowerful its thunderbolt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lady's gonna do something!\NWe might wanna get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt... Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, Grandma. That's an\Nincredible thunderbolt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, are we gonna be\Nokay under this umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me. You'll be fine as long as you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's attacking everyone! We'll die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you hit Sogeking, Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't take it out on me.\NThe problem lies in how you're using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Usopp-kun says that he\Ndoesn't remember adding that feature!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that thing is crazy powerful!\NYou brought down a bunch of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah...\N--Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to him, Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You apologize, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! That reminded me of the\Nshock I had the first time I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that girl was here just\Nfor support, but she sure can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate lady, you're incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you guys're okay, too, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no accident that I've lived\Nfor several decades, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's that idiot\Nwho rushed out by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me... This island isn't small,\Nso if we are to find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's go after him, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're mere pirates...\NHow dare they make a ruckus...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped onto the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those jerks! This is endless!\NI can't move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're running in the opposite direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of you guys, head to\Nthe main island front gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates broke open the gate and\Nare invading! Stop them at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be here! Good!\NThat makes things quite a bit easier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's over there! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, it was this way, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it wouldn't be good if you led the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine if we go straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that darn idiot!\NHe rushed out by himself, as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our sticking with that idiot\Nmakes us quite the idiots as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to Luffy, it seems that the\Nmarines are scattered for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So all we have to do now is\Nhead straight to the courthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, my chronic disease is coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna die, you can remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's cured now!\N--That's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Watchdogs are ordered\Nto guard the front gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can cross this line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up, you damn rogues!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doggie policemen, this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that it's just us, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're completely surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I look a little closer,\Nthere are too many enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the jig is up, pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are cocky! Guys, get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you could've at least\Nlet us have a little fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget why you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't where you should\Nbe focusing your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that it'd take a whole\Nday to fight this many enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're quite energetic. Don't die, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guards! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a King Bull from Water Seven!\NPrepare the cannons immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watchdogs! Get back in formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you go!\NOur dogs are faster than your fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! They're gonna try jumping on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can't we go faster?!\N--Hey, cook guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see... those guys, tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You guys're fired."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump onto it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave them to you, Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll skewer you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half Knot Air Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! S-Some Watchdogs were taken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools! They let their guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way ordinary people\Ncan match our speed. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pierce you before you notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More went down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that your temperament\Nhasn't changed at all, huh, Cutty Flam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had realized sooner that you\Nwere alive and had the blueprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have had to go\Nthrough all this trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since we could just have brought\Nyou in for your past crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, your older fellow\Ndisciple Iceberg was a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Tom died,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he brought the shipbuilding\Ncompanies in Water Seven together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and organized a big company\Nby himself. And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he approached the World Government,\Nwhich he must've had a grudge against,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and soon his company established its position
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a purveyor to the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the president of the\Nshipbuilding company Galley-La
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the mayor of the\Ncity of water, Water Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After he became a figure\Nthat everyone supported
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that was indispensable to the Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we couldn't meddle with him carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that your company contracts to\Nbuild ships for the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break! I'm not gonna tolerate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why he's been\Ncontracting with the Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a smart man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the winds started blowing in my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I couldn't wait any longer and\Nwas about to take forceful measures...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Admiral Aokiji sent me the good news...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Nico Robin was headed\Nto Water Seven on a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drank a cup of coffee to calm myself down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put all the conditions, including\NBuster Call, into the plan of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there was a bit of change in the plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but look! Both triggers for the\Nancient weapon's revival are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it? The winds the entire\Nworld over are blowing in my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:21:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A power strong enough to give me control\Nover any large country I might desire
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is in my hands now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Aokiji give you the\Nauthority to exercise Buster Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no position to ask me\Nquestions, you insolent woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't recognized\Nthe value of your existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would've been practically worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should appreciate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, the repugnant kin of Ohara,\Nthe land of devils...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:07.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:11.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:15.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll become No. 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll aim for freedom in wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's a faint light\Nshowing us the road to tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,an era created by risking everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We always try our best, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:31.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to achieve glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,now is the time--don't be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll surely win the future\Ntogether with friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:39.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we start running faster\Ntowards the vast world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:43.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take off with unknown powers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't fear, and we don't waver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:49.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nin the end we'll surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:53.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:57.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:01.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start running towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:08.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's not what we agreed upon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the Straw Hats would\Nleave Water Seven safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left Water Seven safely...\Nand so, now, they're here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Robin Betrayed! The Motive\Nof the World Government!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
